#: ../../library/bz2.rst:76
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The *mode* argument can be either ``'r'`` for reading (default), ``'w'`` for"
" overwriting, ``'x'`` for exclusive creation, or ``'a'`` for appending. "
"These can equivalently be given as ``'rb'``, ``'wb'``, ``'xb'`` and ``'ab'``"
